archimate:BusinessObject.name: Syntax Encoding Scheme
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
A set of strings and an associated set of rules that describe a mapping between that set of strings and a set of resources. The mapping rules may define how the string is structured or they may simply enumerate all the strings and the corresponding resources.
Source: W3C http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Datatype
